quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,89,"“Kandi yemwe bantu banjye! Urwango mumfitiye ntiruzatume mugerwaho n’ibihano nk’ibyageze ku bantu ba Nuhu, cyangwa abantu ba Hudu, cyangwa se abantu ba Swaleh. Kandi abantu ba Loti ntibari kure yanyu (kuko nta gihe gishize barimbuwe ndetse bakaba bari abaturanyi banyu).”"
  11,90,"“Munasabe Nyagasani wanyu kubababarira ndetse munamwicuzeho. Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wanjye ni Nyirimpuhwe zihebuje, Uwuje urukundo (ku wicuza).”"
  11,91,"Baravuga bati “Yewe Shuwayibu! Ntidusobanukirwa byinshi mu byo uvuga, kandi mu by’ukuri tubona ari wowe munyantege nke muri twe. Ndetse iyo bitaba (kubaha) umuryango wawe, twari kukwicisha amabuye kandi ntiwatunanira.”"
  11,92,(Shuwayibu) aravuga ati “Yemwe bantu banjye! None se umuryango wanjye ni wo muha agaciro kurusha Allah mwateye umugongo? Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wanjye azi neza ibyo mukora.”
  11,93,"“Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimukore uko mubishaka nanjye ndakora (nk’uko Allah yantegetse). Rwose muzamenya uzagerwaho n’ibihano bimusuzuguza ndetse n’umubeshyi. Bityo ngaho nimutegereze, mu by’ukuri ndi kumwe namwe mu bategereje.”"
  11,94,"Maze ubwo isezerano ryacu (ryo guhana abigometse) ryasohoraga, twarokoye Shuwayibu n’abemeye hamwe na we ku bw’impuhwe ziduturutseho, nuko ab’inkozi z’ibibi bakubitwa n’urusaku (rw’ibihano), maze bahinduka imirambo bapfukamye mu mazu yabo"
  11,95,Bamera nk’aho batigeze bayabamo. Nta gushidikanya ko mu by’ukuri abantu b’i Madiyani boramye nk’uko aba Thamud boramye
  11,96,Mu by’ukuri twohereje Musa (azanye) ibitangaza byacu n’ibimenyetso bigaragara
  11,97,"(Twamwohereje) kwa Farawo n’ibyegera bye, ariko bakurikiye itegeko rya Farawo, nyamara itegeko rya Farawo nta shingiro ryari ryifite"